  "The chain rule states that the derivative of a composite function f(g(x)) is f'(g(x)) * g'(x). You differentiate the outer function evaluated at the inner function, then multiply by the derivative of the inner function.": "链条规则规定,复合函数f(g(x))的衍生物是f'(g(x)) *g(x)。您区分了在内部函数中评价的外部函数,然后乘以内部函数的衍生物。",
